OL,6,FDelivering the verdict, the judge
OL,7,Freferenced Edwards' mental health as
OL,8,Fpotentially impairing his 'decision
OL,9,Fmaking', as ITV News Correspondent
OL,10,FJohn Ray reports
OL,12,FDisgraced former BBC presenter Huw
OL,13,FEdwards has been sentenced to six
OL,14,Fmonths imprisonment, suspended for two
OL,15,Fyears, after pleading guilty to
OL,16,Faccessing indecent images of children
OL,17,Fas young as seven.
