OL,3,CHuw Edwards given six month suspended
OL,4,Csentence
OL,6,FIn July, the former broadcaster
OL,7,Fadmitted three charges of "making"
OL,8,Findecent photographs after convicted
OL,9,Fpaedophile Alex Williams sent him 41
OL,10,Fillegal images over WhatsApp.
OL,12,FThe chief magistrate, District Judge
OL,13,FPaul Goldspring, went through the
OL,14,Fmitigating factors he was taking into
OL,15,Faccount in sentencing Edwards.
OL,17,FHe said he believed the former
OL,18,Fbroadcaster's remorse was genuine and
OL,19,Fthat his mental health at the time of
OL,20,Fthe offences could have impaired his
OL,21,Fdecision-making.
