OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer said it
OL,7,Fwas "for the court to decide" Edwards'
OL,8,Fsentence and that he was "shocked and
OL,9,Fappalled" by the case.
OL,11,FSpeaking to reporters in Rome, Starmer
OL,12,Fsaid: "I'm really shocked in relation
OL,13,Fto the Huw Edwards case, really
OL,14,Fshocked and appalled, as I'm sure
OL,15,Feverybody who has read or looked at it
OL,16,Fis."
